{"tid":1764740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拒受勳退休社工：年輕人心水清","createTime":"2019-12-01T10:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T12:33:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b0455d7b9df69e369cbfe0b89a1ccd409f7035fe","tid":1764740,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:28:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191201/U6XLKX2222AZSCHMKMGJP6QPJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191201%2FU6XLKX2222AZSCHMKMGJP6QPJM%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=7cb8ded5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191201%2FU6XLKX2222AZSCHMKMGJP6QPJM%2F&h=28d150ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191201/U6XLKX2222AZSCHMKMGJP6QPJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n拒受勳退休社工：年輕人心水清<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191201/large/1575129681_499a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575129681_499a.jpg&h=dbc6b77c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港基督教服務處前總幹事孫勵生（圖）早前拒絕接受林鄭月娥授勳，昨日他出席「中學生&times;銀髮族集會」發言時透露，拒絕受勳後收到不少指摘，連遠在海外的老師也稱他為「母校敗類」，「為需要負上刑責的青年開脫」。<br />\n<br />\n曾任職社工36年的他表示，社會標籤年輕人為「廢青」、「憤青」、「邊青」、「隱青」，但他認為年輕人是「心水清」，對於多方指摘，他感覺夏蟲不可語冰，「佢哋好難明年輕人唔係唔求長進，唔係唔爭氣，而係香港呢種缺陷制度、貪婪嘅社會，呢種不公義社會環境造就呢種所謂廢青、憤青、隱青嘅現象」。他曾與朋友討論，如何改變這些人的思維，也反問年輕人，有否想過如何令這班人感到羞愧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勉勵力量微小仍可放光芒<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警屢改傷者數字 難解打死人疑團<br />\n<br />\n他認為年輕人有三件事可以做，一是保持公民素質，在其革新精神加上「尊重多元、仁愛公義」等普世價值，一定能爭取明白普世價值的文明世界掌聲；二是充實自己，他期望年輕人未來10年，不要荒廢學業和光陰，用興趣和潛能展現青春、貢獻香港；三是投入社區，以創意重建社區面貌，在不同方面用真正行動去「掌摑」指摘他們是憤青、廢青的人。<br />\n<br />\n最後，他引述清代詩人袁枚短詩《苔》指出，牡丹是富貴人家喜愛的花，人們見到台階上的青苔恨不得鏟走它，不過「苔花如米小，也學牡丹開」，勉勵年輕人力量微小仍可綻放光芒。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙、陳詠恩"},{"pid":"d898e252e9871b36a0baf33d613ede754da29e4f","tid":1764740,"uid":337761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"外媒記者有報<br />\n今日警察向和平示威者噴胡椒tg<br />\n快啲推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入 －》<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=5e56331a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"2e22aaa4f19895144b63145e3ca8e611dfa31da3","tid":1764740,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4804b97a950936eddfd4e3f5ad274aa00da16bb8","tid":1764740,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"外媒記者有報<br />\n今日警察向和平示威者噴胡椒tg<br />\n快啲推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=5e56331a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"9a3f0d0d848f2b3592ad9aaade048ef5aacfddf5","tid":1764740,"uid":52358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"連遠在海外的老師也稱他為「母校敗類」<br />\n關你班離地廢老撚事咩"},{"pid":"a535de289c7175fd8e5b7483cca2a71d1f986dc5","tid":1764740,"uid":55010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"勵生好嘢，林鄭正垃圾"}]}